ygData.subject: Re: Good places for hunting for 18th level
ygData.msgSnippet: Oasis. Crocs and caimans etc can be soloed. You may have to go look under water along the beach (tween docks and pillars worked for me) to find one, pull then
ygData.messageBody:
Oasis. Crocs and caimans etc can be soloed.

You may have to go look under water along the beach (tween docks and pillars worked for me) to find one, pull then run onto the beach and it will follow.

Maybe you can do minos in Beholder gorge but not for sure.

Theres a nice bug spot in EKarana at the bottom of the ramp from Highpass and you can do Crushbone orcs.

Shannyn t'Daisemi


>>> "T'n-D'rl" <tndrl@...> 02/02/00 07:20PM >>>

go on for a total of maybe 4 hours a week. Any suggestions to maximize

leaving the group abruptly and that's not fair to them. Any help would
be appreciated.

Qanadar, Cleric of Tunare, Karana
